column2: SELECT U.up_id, S.*  FROM #upLoad U CROSS APPLY (SELECT Objid FROM   dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( U.up_ra ,U.up_dec ,U.up_sep )) S  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, p.g,p.i,p.r,p.u,p.z,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  ( p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
